Test Suite: Authentication & User Registration 

Target Application: Automation Exercise Module: Signup / Login Test Level: System Testing & UI Validation Execution Type: Manual 

📝 Suite Overview 

This test suite validates the front-end validation, backend data integrity, and error handling of the primary authentication gateway. It includes positive flows, negative boundary tests, and basic security checks. 

 

